Conergy AG, a German maker of solar
energy components, signed contracts to build 5 megawatts of
projects in the U.S.  Conergy will build four photovoltaic projects in  California 
with a combined capacity of 3 megawatts, a 1.8-megawatt plant in
Pennsylvania and a commercial rooftop unit in  Hawaii  in
contracts signed last month, the Hamburg-based company said in
an e-mailed statement today. It didnâ€™t identify the other
